reviewText: Corina is the queen of stringer control. You will learn heat control, stringer control and have fun in the process. Great information here.

The information presented in this dvd is INDISPENSABLE for a bead-maker. Unfortunately, it now sits unwatched on my shelf.  I would rather rent it than own it, but it is what it is. My beads honestly wouldn't be HALF as good if I had never watched it.
